-... but don't want to hear "Rock-a-Bye Baby" for the thousandth time?

Enjoy modern lullabies that will reliably soothe you and your baby gently to sleep. To fall asleep, children need to feel safe. The soothing sleep music composed especially for babies and their parents helps you create a snug, secure atmosphere.

The unique soundscapes (piano, keyboard, guitar) satisfy our human need for security and relaxation. They are based on scientific studies that demonstrate the positive effects of music on our sleeping habits. In combination with the music, you will also hear the sound of ocean waves gently lapping at the shore. Ocean sounds are well loved by babies as they simulate their pre-birth experience in the womb, which babies remember fondly. The sound of the waves comforts them and promotes even, harmonious breathing.

This premium audiobook contains:
Eleven unique sleep tracks with a running time of over 120 minutes, composed by certified music therapists and played at the same rhythm as the resting heart rate. In addition, there are comforting nature sounds that satisfy our human need for security and relaxation.

- Are you looking for peaceful, soothing music your baby can fall asleep to ...

-... but don't want to hear "Rock-a-Bye Baby" for the thousandth time?

Enjoy modern lullabies that will reliably soothe you and your baby gently to sleep. To fall asleep, children need to feel safe. The soothing sleep music composed especially for babies and their parents helps you create a snug, secure atmosphere.

The unique soundscapes (piano, keyboard, guitar) satisfy our human need for security and relaxation. They are based on scientific studies that demonstrate the positive effects of music on our sleeping habits. In combination with the music, you will also hear the sound of ocean waves gently lapping at the shore. Ocean sounds are well loved by babies as they simulate their pre-birth experience in the womb, which babies remember fondly. The sound of the waves comforts them and promotes even, harmonious breathing.

This premium audiobook contains:
Eleven unique sleep tracks with a running time of over 120 minutes, composed by certified music therapists and played at the same rhythm as the resting heart rate. In addition, there are comforting nature sounds that satisfy our human need for security and relaxation.
